<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Abhishek Sharma — Software Engineer | UI/UX Designer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bricolage+Grotesque:opsz,wght@12..96,200..800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#060608;--bg2:#0e0e12;--bg3:#16161c;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);--border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
  --text:#f0f0f4;--muted:#7a7a8a;
  --accent:#e8ff47;--accent-rgb:232,255,71;
  --glow:rgba(232,255,71,0.18);
  --font-display:'Bricolage Grotesque',sans-serif;
  --font-body:'Inter',sans-serif;
}
.theme-aurora{--accent:#00f5d4;--accent-rgb:0,245,212;--glow:rgba(0,245,212,0.18)}
.theme-nova{--accent:#a78bfa;--accent-rgb:167,139,250;--glow:rgba(167,139,250,0.18)}
.theme-ember{--accent:#ff6b35;--accent-rgb:255,107,53;--glow:rgba(255,107,53,0.18)}
.theme-frost{--accent:#7dd3fc;--accent-rgb:125,211,252;--glow:rgba(125,211,252,0.18)}

html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;cursor:none}

/* CUSTOM CURSOR */
#cursor{position:fixed;width:12px;height:12px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:transform 0.1s,background 0.3s,width 0.3s,height 0.3s;mix-blend-mode:difference}
#cursor-trail{position:fixed;width:36px;height:36px;border:1.5px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.4);border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9998;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:left 0.12s ease,top 0.12s ease,width 0.3s,height 0.3s,border-color 0.3s}
body:hover #cursor{opacity:1}

/* SPARKS CANVAS */
#sparks-canvas{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none;z-index:9990}

/* THREE.JS HERO CANVAS */
#hero-canvas{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0}

/* PAGE SYSTEM */
.page{display:none;min-height:100vh;opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px) scale(0.99);transition:opacity 0.5s ease,transform 0.5s ease}
.page.active{display:block;opacity:1;transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:200;padding:18px 40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:rgba(6,6,8,0.7);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:-0.5px;position:relative}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--accent);transition:color 0.3s}
.nav-logo::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-2px;left:0;width:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent);transition:width 0.3s}
.nav-logo:hover::after{width:100%}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-style:none;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:500;transition:color 0.2s;cursor:pointer;position:relative}
.nav-links a::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-3px;left:0;width:0;height:1.5px;background:var(--accent);transition:width 0.3s}
.nav-links a:hover,.nav-links a.active{color:var(--text)}
.nav-links a:hover::after,.nav-links a.active::after{width:100%}

/* THEME SWITCHER */
.theme-switcher{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:center}
.theme-dot{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;cursor:pointer;border:2px solid transparent;transition:transform 0.2s,border-color 0.2s}
.theme-dot:hover,.theme-dot.active{transform:scale(1.3);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5)}
.td-void{background:#e8ff47}
.td-aurora{background:#00f5d4}
.td-nova{background:#a78bfa}
.td-ember{background:#ff6b35}
.td-frost{background:#7dd3fc}

/* MUSIC PLAYER */
.music-btn{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 14px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid var(--border2);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:var(--muted);font-size:0.78rem;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:var(--font-body)}
.music-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.music-bars{display:flex;gap:2px;align-items:flex-end;height:14px}
.music-bar{width:3px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:2px;animation:none;opacity:0.4}
.music-btn.playing .music-bar{opacity:1}
.music-btn.playing .music-bar:nth-child(1){animation:bar1 0.8s ease infinite}
.music-btn.playing .music-bar:nth-child(2){animation:bar2 0.6s ease infinite}
.music-btn.playing .music-bar:nth-child(3){animation:bar3 0.9s ease infinite}
@keyframes bar1{0%,100%{height:4px}50%{height:12px}}
@keyframes bar2{0%,100%{height:10px}50%{height:4px}}
@keyframes bar3{0%,100%{height:6px}50%{height:14px}}

/* HERO */
.hero-wrap{position:relative;height:100vh;min-height:680px;overflow:hidden;display:flex;align-items:center}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:10;padding:0 60px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;width:100%}
.hero-tag{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.hero-tag::before{content:'';display:inline-block;width:28px;height:1.5px;background:var(--accent)}
.hero h1{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(3rem,6.5vw,6rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-0.04em;margin-bottom:28px;max-width:900px}
.hero h1 .word{display:inline-block;overflow:hidden}
.hero h1 .word span{display:inline-block;transform:translateY(110%);animation:wordReveal 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) forwards}
.hero h1 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--accent);transition:color 0.5s}
@keyframes wordReveal{to{transform:translateY(0)}}
.hero-desc{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem;max-width:540px;margin-bottom:44px;line-height:1.75;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 0.8s 0.7s ease forwards}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 0.8s 0.9s ease forwards}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

/* AVAILABLE BADGE */
.avail-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:100px;background:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.08);border:1px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.25);color:var(--accent);font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:28px;transition:background 0.3s,border-color 0.3s,color 0.3s}
.avail-dot{width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s infinite;transition:background 0.3s}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:0.4;transform:scale(0.8)}}

/* BUTTONS */
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:100px;font-weight:600;font-size:0.88rem;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.25s;border:none;font-family:var(--font-body);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.btn::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;width:0;height:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);border-radius:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);transition:width 0.5s,height 0.5s}
.btn:hover::before{width:300px;height:300px}
.btn-primary{background:var(--text);color:#000}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent)}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border2)}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}

/* SCROLLING TEXT */
.marquee-wrap{overflow:hidden;border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:16px 0;margin:0}
.marquee-track{display:flex;gap:36px;white-space:nowrap;animation:marquee 22s linear infinite}
.marquee-track:hover{animation-play-state:paused}
.marquee-item{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--muted);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;transition:color 0.3s}
.marquee-item:hover{color:var(--accent)}
.marquee-item::before{content:'✦';color:var(--accent);font-size:0.65rem}
@keyframes marquee{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}

/* SECTIONS */
.section{padding:100px 60px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.section-label{font-size:0.75rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.section-label::before{content:'';display:inline-block;width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--accent)}
.section-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.8rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;margin-bottom:56px}
.section-title span{color:var(--accent);transition:color 0.3s}

/* ABOUT STRIP */
.about-strip{background:var(--bg2);padding:80px 60px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.about-strip-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.about-big-text{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.8vw,2.1rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.45;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text)}
.about-big-text strong{color:var(--accent);transition:color 0.3s}

/* PROJECTS GRID */
.projects-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:20px}
.project-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;display:block;transform-style:preserve-3d;transition:box-shadow 0.3s,border-color 0.3s;will-change:transform}
.project-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2);box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 0 40px rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.06)}
.project-card-inner{position:relative}
.project-card img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform 0.5s ease}
.project-card:hover img{transform:scale(1.04)}
.project-card-shine{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at var(--mx,50%) var(--my,50%),rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 0%,transparent 60%);pointer-events:none;transition:opacity 0.3s;opacity:0}
.project-card:hover .project-card-shine{opacity:1}
.project-card-body{padding:20px}
.project-card-tags{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.tag{font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--muted)}
.project-card-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;transition:color 0.2s}
.project-card:hover .project-card-title{color:var(--accent)}
.project-card-year{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* EXPERTISE */
.expertise-tabs{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.tab-btn{padding:9px 22px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}
.tab-btn.active,.tab-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.06)}
.expertise-content{display:none}
.expertise-content.active{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:center}
.expertise-content img{width:100%;border-radius:14px;aspect-ratio:4/3;object-fit:cover}
.expertise-desc{font-size:0.98rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85}

/* SKILLS */
.skills-row{overflow:hidden;padding:12px 0}
.skills-track{display:flex;gap:14px;animation:marquee 28s linear infinite}
.skills-track.reverse{animation-direction:reverse}
.skill-chip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:9px 16px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:100px;white-space:nowrap;font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:500;transition:border-color 0.2s,color 0.2s,background 0.2s}
.skill-chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.05)}
.skill-chip img{width:18px;height:18px;object-fit:contain}

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.testimonials-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:16px}
.testimonial-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;transition:border-color 0.3s,transform 0.3s,box-shadow 0.3s}
.testimonial-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2);transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
.testimonial-author{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px}
.testimonial-author img{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid var(--border)}
.testimonial-name{font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem}
.testimonial-role{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)}
.testimonial-text{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75}

/* GITHUB REPOS */
.repos-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:0}
.repo-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:20px;transition:border-color 0.2s,transform 0.2s;text-decoration:none;display:block}
.repo-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.repo-name{font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:6px;transition:color 0.2s}
.repo-card:hover .repo-name{color:var(--accent)}
.repo-desc{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px;min-height:36px}
.repo-meta{display:flex;gap:14px;font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)}
.repo-lang{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.lang-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent)}

/* CTA */
.cta-section{text-align:center;padding:120px 40px;background:var(--bg2);border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.cta-section h2{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.8rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:36px}

/* FOOTER */
footer{background:var(--bg);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px 60px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.footer-social{display:flex;gap:20px}
.footer-social a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:0.85rem;transition:color 0.2s}
.footer-social a:hover{color:var(--accent)}
.footer-copy{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* ABOUT PAGE */
.about-hero{padding:140px 60px 80px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center}
.about-hero-img{position:relative}
.about-hero-img img{width:100%;border-radius:18px;aspect-ratio:4/5;object-fit:cover;filter:brightness(0.95)}
.about-hero-img::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:-1px;border-radius:18px;border:1px solid var(--border2);pointer-events:none}
.rotating-badge{position:absolute;bottom:-24px;right:-24px;width:120px;height:120px}
.rotating-badge svg{animation:spin 12s linear infinite}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.exp-item{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;padding:22px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:padding-left 0.2s}
.exp-item:first-child{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.exp-item:hover{padding-left:8px}
.exp-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700}
.exp-company{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--accent);margin-top:4px;transition:color 0.3s}
.exp-period{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:right}

/* PROCESS */
.process-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(190px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden}
.process-item{background:var(--bg);padding:28px 22px;transition:background 0.2s}
.process-item:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.process-num{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-bottom:14px;transition:color 0.3s}
.process-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:0.98rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.process-desc{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}

/* AWARDS */
.awards-list{list-style:none}
.award-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:padding-left 0.2s}
.award-item:first-child{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.award-item:hover{padding-left:8px}
.award-name{font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem}
.award-date{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem}

/* COMMUNITY */
.community-stats{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.stat-box{text-align:center;padding:28px 36px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;flex:1;min-width:130px;transition:border-color 0.2s,transform 0.2s}
.stat-box:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-4px)}
.stat-num{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);transition:color 0.3s}
.stat-label{color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;margin-top:4px}
.community-perks{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:40px}
.perk-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:22px;transition:border-color 0.2s,transform 0.2s}
.perk-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.perk-title{font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:0.93rem}
.perk-desc{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* CONTACT */
.contact-wrap{padding:140px 60px 80px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);overflow:hidden}
.faq-question{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:22px 0;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;gap:20px;transition:color 0.2s}
.faq-question:hover{color:var(--accent)}
.faq-question .faq-icon{color:var(--accent);font-size:1.2rem;transition:transform 0.3s;flex-shrink:0}
.faq-answer{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.4s ease}
.faq-answer p{color:var(--muted);padding-bottom:22px;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:1.75}
.faq-item.open .faq-icon{transform:rotate(45deg)}
.faq-item.open .faq-answer{max-height:220px}
.contact-form{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:48px}
.form-input{width:100%;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:0.92rem;outline:none;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.form-input:focus{border-color:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.5)}
.form-input::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}
.form-status{font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:10px;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:8px;display:none}
.form-status.success{display:block;background:rgba(0,245,100,0.1);color:#00f564;border:1px solid rgba(0,245,100,0.2)}
.form-status.error{display:block;background:rgba(255,80,80,0.1);color:#ff5050;border:1px solid rgba(255,80,80,0.2)}

/* FILTER BAR */
.filter-bar{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.filter-btn{padding:7px 18px;border-radius:100px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;font-family:var(--font-body)}
.filter-btn.active,.filter-btn:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);background:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.06)}
.search-box{margin-left:auto;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:100px;padding:7px 18px;color:var(--text);font-size:0.82rem;outline:none;font-family:var(--font-body);width:180px;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.search-box:focus{border-color:rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.4)}
.search-box::placeholder{color:var(--muted)}

/* SCROLL REVEAL */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(36px) rotateX(8deg);transition:opacity 0.7s ease,transform 0.7s ease}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0) rotateX(0)}

/* VIDEO SECTION */
.video-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:16px;margin-top:0}
.video-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s,transform 0.2s;text-decoration:none;display:block}
.video-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-4px)}
.video-thumb{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block}
.video-info{padding:14px 16px}
.video-title{font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:4px;color:var(--text)}
.video-meta{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)}

/* LOADING SCREEN */
#loader{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--bg);z-index:9997;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:opacity 0.6s ease}
#loader.hidden{opacity:0;pointer-events:none}
.loader-logo{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:3rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:32px;letter-spacing:-2px}
.loader-logo span{color:var(--accent)}
.loader-bar-wrap{width:240px;height:2px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.loader-bar{height:100%;background:var(--accent);width:0;animation:loadBar 2s ease forwards;transition:background 0.3s}
@keyframes loadBar{0%{width:0}60%{width:70%}100%{width:100%}}
.loader-text{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);margin-top:14px;letter-spacing:0.1em}

/* SCROLL INDICATOR */
.scroll-indicator{position:absolute;bottom:36px;left:60px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.08em;z-index:10}
.scroll-line{width:48px;height:1px;background:var(--muted);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.scroll-line::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--accent);animation:scrollLine 2s ease infinite}
@keyframes scrollLine{0%{left:-100%}100%{left:100%}}

/* PARTICLES CANVAS */
#particles-canvas{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:1;pointer-events:none}

/* HERO GLASS */
.hero-glass{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:30%;background:linear-gradient(to top,var(--bg),transparent);z-index:5;pointer-events:none}

/* STATS ROW */
.stats-row{display:flex;gap:48px;margin-top:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:0;animation:fadeUp 0.8s 1.1s ease forwards}
.stat-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.stat-item .num{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);line-height:1}
.stat-item .lbl{font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:0.06em}

@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:14px 20px}.nav-links{gap:18px}
  .hero-content{padding:0 24px}
  .section{padding:60px 24px}
  .about-hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px;padding:120px 24px 60px}
  .expertise-content.active{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  footer{padding:28px 24px}
  .contact-wrap{padding:120px 24px 60px}
  .cta-section{padding:80px 24px}
  .about-strip{padding:50px 24px}
  .stats-row{gap:28px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- LOADING SCREEN -->
<div id="loader">
  <div class="loader-logo">A<span>S</span></div>
  <div class="loader-bar-wrap"><div class="loader-bar" id="loader-bar"></div></div>
  <div class="loader-text">INITIALISING EXPERIENCE</div>
</div>

<!-- CUSTOM CURSOR -->
<div id="cursor"></div>
<div id="cursor-trail"></div>

<!-- SPARKS -->
<canvas id="sparks-canvas"></canvas>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="main-nav">
  <div class="nav-logo" onclick="navigate('home')">A<span>S</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a onclick="navigate('home')" id="nav-home" class="active">Home</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="navigate('about')" id="nav-about">About</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="navigate('projects')" id="nav-projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a onclick="navigate('contact')" id="nav-contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center">
    <div class="theme-switcher">
      <div class="theme-dot td-void active" onclick="setTheme('')" title="Void"></div>
      <div class="theme-dot td-aurora" onclick="setTheme('aurora')" title="Aurora"></div>
      <div class="theme-dot td-nova" onclick="setTheme('nova')" title="Nova"></div>
      <div class="theme-dot td-ember" onclick="setTheme('ember')" title="Ember"></div>
      <div class="theme-dot td-frost" onclick="setTheme('frost')" title="Frost"></div>
    </div>
    <button class="music-btn" id="music-btn" onclick="toggleMusic()">
      <div class="music-bars">
        <div class="music-bar" style="height:8px"></div>
        <div class="music-bar" style="height:12px"></div>
        <div class="music-bar" style="height:6px"></div>
      </div>
      <span id="music-label">Music</span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HOME PAGE -->
<div class="page active" id="page-home">
  <div class="hero-wrap">
    <canvas id="hero-canvas"></canvas>
    <canvas id="particles-canvas"></canvas>
    <div class="hero-glass"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="avail-badge"><div class="avail-dot"></div>Available for work</div>
      <p class="hero-tag">Hey! It's me Abhishek,</p>
      <h1 id="hero-title">Crafting purpose<br/>driven <em>experiences</em><br/>that <em>inspire.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">I work with brands globally to build pixel-perfect, engaging, and accessible digital experiences that drive results and achieve business goals.</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" onclick="navigate('about')">Know me better →</a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline" onclick="navigate('projects')">View Work</a>
      </div>
      <div class="stats-row">
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="num" id="stat-exp">5+</span><span class="lbl">Years Experience</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="num" id="stat-proj">18+</span><span class="lbl">Projects Shipped</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="num" id="stat-comm">5k+</span><span class="lbl">Community Members</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><span class="num" id="stat-gh">—</span><span class="lbl">GitHub Repos</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-indicator">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>SCROLL
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="marquee-wrap">
    <div class="marquee-track" id="marquee-track"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-strip reveal">
    <div class="about-strip-inner">
      <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
      <p class="about-big-text">I'm <strong>Abhishek Sharma</strong>, with over <strong>5+ years</strong> of experience in design & development with strong focus on producing high quality & impactful digital experiences. I have worked with some of the most innovative industry leaders to help build their top-notch products.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label">My Work</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Selected <span>Projects</span></h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:40px;margin-top:-40px">A curated selection showcasing expertise and results.</p>
    <div class="projects-grid" id="featured-projects"></div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:44px">
      <a class="btn btn-outline" onclick="navigate('projects')">View All Projects →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal" style="padding-top:0">
    <p class="section-label">Speciality</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Areas of <span>Expertise</span></h2>
    <div class="expertise-tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('development',this)">Development</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('design',this)">UI/UX Design</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('branding',this)">Branding</button>
    </div>
    <div class="expertise-content active" id="tab-development">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.2">Building robust digital products</h3>
        <p class="expertise-desc">From scalable frontends with React and Next.js to full-stack applications with Node and databases — I craft code that's clean, performant, and maintainable. I specialise in creating fast, accessible web experiences that users love.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="https://devrajchatribin.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdevelopment.avif&w=1200&q=75" alt="Development" loading="lazy"/>
    </div>
    <div class="expertise-content" id="tab-design">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.2">Designing with purpose & precision</h3>
        <p class="expertise-desc">I combine user research with sharp visual thinking to create interfaces that feel intuitive and delightful. From wireframes to high-fidelity Figma prototypes, every pixel is intentional.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="https://devrajchatribin.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdesigning.avif&w=1200&q=75" alt="UI/UX Design" loading="lazy"/>
    </div>
    <div class="expertise-content" id="tab-branding">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.2">Shaping memorable brand identities</h3>
        <p class="expertise-desc">A brand is more than a logo — it's a promise. I help startups and businesses craft cohesive visual identities that resonate with their audience and stand out in their market.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="https://devrajchatribin.com/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbranding.avif&w=1200&q=75" alt="Branding" loading="lazy"/>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div style="overflow:hidden;padding:20px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
    <div class="skills-row"><div class="skills-track" id="skills1"></div></div>
    <div class="skills-row" style="margin-top:10px"><div class="skills-track reverse" id="skills2"></div></div>
  </div>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Open Source</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">GitHub <span>Repositories</span></h2>
    <div class="repos-grid" id="repos-grid"><p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.9rem">Loading repositories…</p></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal" style="padding-top:0">
    <p class="section-label">Testimonials</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What others <span>say</span></h2>
    <div class="testimonials-grid" id="testimonials-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-section reveal">
    <div class="avail-badge" style="margin-bottom:24px"><div class="avail-dot"></div>Available for work</div>
    <h2>Let's create your<br/>next big idea.</h2>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" onclick="navigate('contact')" style="margin-top:8px">Contact Me →</a>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-social">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abhishek-sharma/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/abhishek-sharma" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
      <a href="mailto:abhishek@example.com">Email</a>
    </div>
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 Abhishek Sharma. All rights reserved.</span>
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT PAGE -->
<div class="page" id="page-about">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div>
      <div class="avail-badge" style="margin-bottom:20px"><div class="avail-dot"></div>Creative Developer & Digital Designer</div>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px">Building impactful,<br/>mission-focused websites</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:32px">I collaborate with brands globally to design impactful, mission-focused websites that drive results and achieve business goals. My work sits at the intersection of design thinking and engineering excellence.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">My Resume ↗</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-img">
      <img src="https://devrajchatribin.com/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fhero.0uhybhrq2kj89.webp&w=828&q=75" alt="Abhishek Sharma"/>
      <div class="rotating-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.07)" stroke="rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <path id="textPath2" d="M60,60 m-45,0 a45,45 0 1,1 90,0 a45,45 0 1,1 -90,0"/>
          <text fill="#e8ff47" font-size="9.5" font-family="Inter" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="3.2">
            <textPath href="#textPath2">ABHISHEK SHARMA • SOFTWARE ENGINEER •</textPath>
          </text>
          <text x="50" y="66" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e8ff47" font-size="18">✦</text>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="overflow:hidden;padding:20px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
    <div class="skills-row"><div class="skills-track" id="about-skills1"></div></div>
    <div class="skills-row" style="margin-top:10px"><div class="skills-track reverse" id="about-skills2"></div></div>
  </div>

  <section class="section reveal">
    <p class="section-label">Work History</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
    <div id="experience-list">
      <div class="exp-item"><div><div class="exp-title">OneShield Software</div><div class="exp-company">Software Engineer</div></div><div class="exp-period">Aug 2022 — Present</div></div>
      <div class="exp-item"><div><div class="exp-title">Design and Code</div><div class="exp-company">Founder</div></div><div class="exp-period">Jan 2021 — Present</div></div>
      <div class="exp-item"><div><div class="exp-title">BlackboxAI</div><div class="exp-company">Design Engineer</div></div><div class="exp-period">Feb 2025 — Mar 2025</div></div>
      <div class="exp-item"><div><div class="exp-title">Social3</div><div class="exp-company">UI/UX Designer</div></div><div class="exp-period">Aug 2022 — Sep 2023</div></div>
      <div class="exp-item"><div><div class="exp-title">Ignite Solutions</div><div class="exp-company">Frontend Developer</div></div><div class="exp-period">2021 — 2022</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal" style="padding-top:0">
    <p class="section-label">Steps I Follow</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">My Design <span>Process</span></h2>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-item"><div class="process-num">01.</div><div class="process-title">Strategize</div><p class="process-desc">Plan the details before execution. Research, goals, and roadmap first.</p></div>
      <div class="process-item"><div class="process-num">02.</div><div class="process-title">Wireframe</div><p class="process-desc">Rapid sketches and low-fi wireframes to validate ideas quickly.</p></div>
      <div class="process-item"><div class="process-num">03.</div><div class="process-title">Design</div><p class="process-desc">High-fidelity Figma prototypes with every pixel intentional.</p></div>
      <div class="process-item"><div class="process-num">04.</div><div class="process-title">Develop</div><p class="process-desc">Clean, performant, accessible code that matches the design precisely.</p></div>
      <div class="process-item"><div class="process-num">05.</div><div class="process-title">QA & Ship</div><p class="process-desc">Performance audits, SEO, cross-browser testing, then deploy.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal" style="padding-top:0">
    <p class="section-label">Awards</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Awards & <span>Recognition</span></h2>
    <ul class="awards-list">
      <li class="award-item"><span class="award-name">Star Performer of the Year</span><span class="award-date">May 2021</span></li>
      <li class="award-item"><span class="award-name">Best Beginner Hack</span><span class="award-date">Apr 2021</span></li>
      <li class="award-item"><span class="award-name">Sketch Webpage Contest Winner</span><span class="award-date">Nov 2020</span></li>
      <li class="award-item"><span class="award-name">Best Space App Winner</span><span class="award-date">Sep 2021</span></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal" style="padding-top:0">
    <p class="section-label">Community Work</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Building a <span>Tech Community</span></h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.85;max-width:700px;margin-bottom:40px">I founded Design & Code — a global community connecting designers and developers to learn, innovate, and grow together. We welcome everyone from beginners to industry experts.</p>
    <div class="community-stats">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">5k+</div><div class="stat-label">Community Members</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">20+</div><div class="stat-label">Events Conducted</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">3+</div><div class="stat-label">Years Active</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">18+</div><div class="stat-label">Projects Shipped</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="community-perks">
      <div class="perk-card"><div class="perk-title">Mentoring</div><p class="perk-desc">Get connected with a mentor that helps pave your career path.</p></div>
      <div class="perk-card"><div class="perk-title">Opportunities</div><p class="perk-desc">Internships, job opportunities, and real-world experience.</p></div>
      <div class="perk-card"><div class="perk-title">Free Resources</div><p class="perk-desc">Design and development resources from industry professionals.</p></div>
      <div class="perk-card"><div class="perk-title">Help & Reviews</div><p class="perk-desc">Portfolio and project reviews by industry experts.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-section reveal">
    <div class="avail-badge" style="margin-bottom:24px"><div class="avail-dot"></div>Available for work</div>
    <h2>Let's create your<br/>next big idea.</h2>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" onclick="navigate('contact')" style="margin-top:8px">Contact Me →</a>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-social">
      <a href="#" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a><a href="#" target="_blank">GitHub</a><a href="#" target="_blank">Instagram</a><a href="#">Email</a>
    </div>
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 Abhishek Sharma. All rights reserved.</span>
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- PROJECTS PAGE -->
<div class="page" id="page-projects">
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:140px">
    <p class="section-label">My Work</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Creating next level<br/><span>digital products</span></h2>
    <div class="filter-bar">
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterProjects('all',this)">All</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProjects('development',this)">Development</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProjects('design',this)">Design</button>
      <input class="search-box" type="text" placeholder="Search projects…" oninput="searchProjects(this.value)"/>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-grid" id="all-projects"></div>
  </section>
  <div class="cta-section">
    <div class="avail-badge" style="margin-bottom:24px"><div class="avail-dot"></div>Available for work</div>
    <h2>Let's create your<br/>next big idea.</h2>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" onclick="navigate('contact')" style="margin-top:8px">Contact Me →</a>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-social">
      <a href="#" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a><a href="#" target="_blank">GitHub</a><a href="#" target="_blank">Instagram</a><a href="#">Email</a>
    </div>
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 Abhishek Sharma. All rights reserved.</span>
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- CONTACT PAGE -->
<div class="page" id="page-contact">
  <div class="contact-wrap">
    <p class="section-label">Get In Touch</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.5rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:60px">Have<br/><span style="color:var(--accent)">Questions?</span></h1>
    <ul class="faq-list" style="margin-bottom:60px">
      <li class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;margin-right:auto">01.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;What is your current role?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>I'm currently working as a Software Engineer at OneShield Software, building enterprise-grade insurance software. I'm also the founder of Design & Code, a global community connecting designers and developers.</p></div></li>
      <li class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;margin-right:auto">02.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;How much does a high-performing website cost?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Cost varies by scope, complexity, and timeline. Simple landing pages start from a few hundred dollars; full-featured web applications range higher. I provide a detailed quote after understanding your requirements.</p></div></li>
      <li class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;margin-right:auto">03.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;How long does a project take start to finish?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>A simple landing page typically takes 1–2 weeks. Complex web applications can take 4–12 weeks. I always deliver on time and keep you updated throughout the process.</p></div></li>
      <li class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:0.82rem;font-family:var(--font-body);font-weight:400;margin-right:auto">04.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Are you available full-time?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>I'm open to discussing full-time opportunities that align with my skills and passion for design and development. Feel free to reach out via LinkedIn or email to start a conversation.</p></div></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="contact-form">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px">Get in touch</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:36px">Reach out for projects, collaborations, or just to say hi.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px">
        <input type="text" id="cf-name" class="form-input" placeholder="Your Name"/>
        <input type="email" id="cf-email" class="form-input" placeholder="Your Email"/>
        <input type="text" id="cf-subject" class="form-input" placeholder="Subject"/>
        <textarea id="cf-msg" class="form-input" placeholder="Tell me about your project…" rows="5" style="resize:vertical"></textarea>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="submitForm()" style="align-self:flex-start">Send Message →</button>
        <div class="form-status" id="form-status"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-social">
      <a href="#" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a><a href="#" target="_blank">GitHub</a><a href="#" target="_blank">Instagram</a><a href="#">Email</a>
    </div>
    <span class="footer-copy">© 2026 Abhishek Sharma. All rights reserved.</span>
  </footer>
